266
0:10:59.26,000 --> 0:11:01,000
I was doing a pathetically slow speed

267
0:11:01.26,000 --> 0:11:03,000
of about 1.3 knots,

268
0:11:03.26,000 --> 0:11:06,000
and they were doing only marginally less pathetic speed of about 1.4:

269
0:11:06.26,000 --> 0:11:09,000
it was like two snails in a mating dance.

270
0:11:09.26,000 --> 0:11:11,000
But, eventually, we did manage to meet up

271
0:11:11.26,000 --> 0:11:13,000
